  <brief_title>Intramuscular Benzathine Penicillin Injection Procedure</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use of Virtual Reality and Distraction Cards to Reduce Pain During Intramuscular Benzathine Penicillin Injection Procedure in Adults: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
